dct_title_s: Plano del Puerto de Sn. Carlos
dct_description_sm: trabajado Aabordo de las Corvetas descubierta y atrevida de la Marina Real ; Antonio Vazqz. la gr[abó].
Relief shown pictorially and depths shown by bathymetric soundings.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Bar scale on map in "millas Maritimas."
Shows coastline, topography, vegetation, drainage, islands, shoals, ports, fortifications.
